⚡️Situation in Ingushetia at this moment:

– In the center of Karabulak, the cleanup of an apartment building in which militants are hiding continues;

– Presumably, the criminal group consists of six people, one of whom is wanted for an attack on law enforcement officers last spring;

– The bandits barricaded themselves in the apartment of the house, and responded to the offer to surrender with shooting;

– The militants are armed with a large number of automatic weapons and explosive devices, grenades are used during the clashes, and FSB special forces are working;

– The active phase of the firefight took place from 19:30 to 21:00 last night; Then throughout the night there were periodic clashes, by this hour the shooting had completely stopped;

– The terrorists tried to escape from the window using a rope, but they failed;

– The blocked militants intended to commit high-profile terrorist crimes;

–At the moment, civilians of the republic were not harmed during the CTO.@opersvodki

